</strong></p></section></section></section></section><section style="text-align: justify;font-size: 14px;color: rgb(62, 62, 62);letter-spacing: 1.5px;line-height: 1.7;padding: 0px 20px;box-sizing: border-box;" powered-by="xiumi.us"><p style="white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;">（1）梦想是对未来美好生活的愿望。梦想总是指向未来，表现为奋斗目标。</p><p style="white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;">（2）编织人生梦想，是青少年时期的重要生命主题。</p><p style="white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;">（3）梦想能不断激发我们生命的热情和勇气，让生活更有色彩。有梦想，就有希望。</p><p style="white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;">（4）人类需要少年的梦想，有了这样的梦想，人类才能不断进步和发展。</p><p style="white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;">（5）明确的人生目标，能够帮助我们在人生的茫茫大海中找到前进的方向。</p></section></section></section><section style="margin: 10px 0%;box-sizing: border-box;" powered-by="xiumi.us"><section style="display: inline-block;width: 100%;vertical-align: top;border-width: 1px;border-style: dashed;border-color: rgb(231, 35, 18);background-color: rgb(255, 246, 246);padding: 16px 20px;box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;" powered-by="xiumi.us"><section style="display: flex;flex-flow: row nowrap;box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="display: inline-block;vertical-align: top;width: 15px;flex: 0 0 auto;align-self: flex-start;height: auto;box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="text-align: left;justify-content: flex-start;margin: 9px 0% 0px;transform: translate3d(-5px, 0px, 0px);-webkit-transform: translate3d(-5px, 0px, 0px);-moz-transform: translate3d(-5px, 0px, 0px);-o-transform: translate3d(-5px, 0px, 0px);box-sizing: border-box;" powered-by="xiumi.us"><section style="display: inline-block;width: 9px;height: 9px;vertical-align: top;overflow: hidden;border-width: 0px;border-style: none;border-color: rgb(62, 62, 62);background-color: rgb(255, 206, 82);box-sizing: border-box;"><section><svg viewBox="0 0 1 1" style="float