t;justify-content: flex-start;margin: 9px 0% 0px;transform: translate3d(-5px, 0px, 0px);-webkit-transform: translate3d(-5px, 0px, 0px);-moz-transform: translate3d(-5px, 0px, 0px);-o-transform: translate3d(-5px, 0px, 0px);box-sizing: border-box;" powered-by="xiumi.us"><section style="display: inline-block;width: 9px;height: 9px;vertical-align: top;overflow: hidden;border-width: 0px;border-style: none;border-color: rgb(62, 62, 62);background-color: rgb(255, 206, 82);box-sizing: border-box;"><section><svg viewBox="0 0 1 1" style="float:left;line-height:0;width:0;vertical-align:top;"></svg></section></section></section></section><section style="display: inline-block;vertical-align: top;width: auto;flex: 100 100 0%;align-self: flex-start;height: auto;box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="font-size: 14px;color: rgb(180, 31, 6);padding: 0px 10px;line-height: 1.7;letter-spacing: 1.5px;box-sizing: border-box;" powered-by="xiumi.us"><p style="text-align: left;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"><em style="box-sizing: border-box;">15.学习对我们生存、生活和成长有什么重要意义？</em></strong></p></section></section></section></section><section style="text-align: justify;font-size: 14px;color: rgb(62, 62, 62);letter-spacing: 1.5px;line-height: 1.7;padding: 0px 20px;box-sizing: border-box;" powered-by="xiumi.us"><p style="white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;">（1）学习，不仅让我们能够生存，而且让我们能够拥有更充实的生活。</p><p style="white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;">（2）学习，打开了生命的视窗，让我们面前的世界变得更广阔、更精彩。</p><p style="white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;">（3）学习，拓展了新的通道，让我们体验不同的生活方式。</p><p style="white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;">（4）学习，改变了思维方式和行为，提升我们的能力和智慧。</p><p style="white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;">（5）学习，带来了更多的选择，让我们变得更加独立和自由。</p><p style="white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;">（6）学习，点亮我们心中的明灯，激发前进的动力。</p><p style="white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;">（7）在学习中，我们分享生命经验，获得成长。</p><p style="white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;">（8）学习，也可以帮助他人，服务社会，为幸福生活奠基。</p></section></section></section><section style="margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;box-sizing: border-box;" powered-by="xiumi.us"><section style="max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img __bg_gif" data-ratio="0.0357698" data-src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_gif/AlBREI3dtiamdX4ghbksyEyoGVWw4icVoIWPqy3BD9r205ocHvlN1bibK1uIYQ89PBHnuermLiaqtsEKOw8tr7AqHA/640?wx_fmt=gif" data-type="gif" data-w="643" style="vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; display: initial; visibility: visible !important; height: auto !important; width: 643px !important;" data-index="17" data-origin-display="" _width="643px" data-order="5" alt="" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_gif/AlBREI3dtiamdX4ghbksyEyoGVWw4icVoIWPqy3BD9r205ocHvlN1bibK1uIYQ89PBHnuermLiaqtsEKOw8tr7AqHA/640?wx_fmt=gif&amp;wxfrom=5&amp;wx_lazy=1" data-fail="0"></section></section><section style="margin: 10px 0%;box-sizing: border-box;" powered-by="xiumi.us"><section style="display: inline-block;width: 100%;vertical-align: top;border-width: 1px;border-style: dashed;border-color: rgb(231, 35, 18);background-color: rgb(255, 246, 246);padding: 16px 20px;box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;" powered-by="xiumi.us"><section style="display: flex;flex-flow: row nowrap;box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="display: inline-block;vertical-align: top;width: 15px;flex: 0 0 auto;align-self: flex-start;height: auto;box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="text-align: left;justify-content: flex-start;margin: 9px 0% 0px;transform: translate3d(-5px, 0px, 0px);-webkit-transform: translate3d(-5px, 0px, 0px);-moz-transform: translate3d(-5px, 0px, 0px);-o-transform: 