;flex-flow: row nowrap;box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="display: inline-block;vertical-align: top;width: 15px;flex: 0 0 auto;align-self: flex-start;height: auto;box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="text-align: left;justify-content: flex-start;margin: 9px 0% 0px;transform: translate3d(-5px, 0px, 0px);-webkit-transform: translate3d(-5px, 0px, 0px);-moz-transform: translate3d(-5px, 0px, 0px);-o-transform: translate3d(-5px, 0px, 0px);box-sizing: border-box;" powered-by="xiumi.us"><section style="display: inline-block;width: 9px;height: 9px;vertical-align: top;overflow: hidden;border-width: 0px;border-style: none;border-color: rgb(62, 62, 62);background-color: rgb(255, 206, 82);box-sizing: border-box;"><section><svg viewBox="0 0 1 1" style="float:left;line-height:0;width:0;vertical-align:top;"></svg></section></section></section></section><section style="display: inline-block;vertical-align: top;width: auto;flex: 100 100 0%;align-self: flex-start;height: auto;box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="font-size: 14px;color: rgb(180, 31, 6);padding: 0px 10px;line-height: 1.7;letter-spacing: 1.5px;box-sizing: border-box;" powered-by="xiumi.us"><p style="text-align: left;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"><em style="box-sizing: border-box;">20.认识自己的内容和途径各有哪些？</em></strong></p></section></section></section></section><section style="text-align: justify;font-size: 14px;color: rgb(62, 62, 62);letter-spacing: 1.5px;line-height: 1.7;padding: 0px 20px;box-sizing: border-box;" powered-by="xiumi.us"><p style="white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;">（1）内容：</p><p style="white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;">我们可以从生理、心理、社会等方面认识自己：可以从身体特征和生理状况来认识自己；可以从个性心理特征来认识自己；可以从在群体中的关系来认识自己；等等。</p><p style="white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;">（2）途径：</p><p style="white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;">①通过自我评价认识自己：自我评价是一个人对自己的判断，最能代表认识自己的水平。对自己有一个恰当的自我评价，能帮助我们接受自己，能帮助我们调节和控制自己的行为。</p><p style="white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;">②通过他人评价认识自己：他人评价是我们认识自己的一面镜子。他人评价有助于我们形成对自己更为客观、完整、清晰的认识。</p></section></section></section><section style="margin: 10px 0%;box-sizing: border-box;" powered-by="xiumi.us"><section style="display: inline-block;width: 100%;vertical-align: top;border-width: 1px;border-style: dashed;border-color: rgb(231, 35, 18);background-color: rgb(255, 246, 246);padding: 16px 20px;box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;" powered-by="xiumi.us"><section style="display: flex;flex-flow: row nowrap;box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="display: inline-block;vertical-align: top;width: 15px;flex: 0 0 auto;align-self: flex-start;height: auto;box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="text-align: left;justify-content: flex-start;margin: 9px 0% 0px;transform: translate3d(-5px, 0px, 0px);-webkit-transform: translate3d(-5px, 0px, 0px);-moz-transform: translate3d(-5px, 0px, 0px);-o-transform: translate3d(-5px, 0px, 0px);box-sizing: border-box;" powered-by="xiumi.us"><section style="display: inline-block;width: 9px;height: 9px;vertical-align: top;overflow: hidden;border-width: 0px;border-style: none;border-color: rgb(62, 62, 62);background-color: rgb(255, 206, 82);box-sizing: border-box;"><section><svg viewBox="0 0 1 1" style="float:left;line-height:0;width:0;vertical-align:top;"></svg></section></section></section></section><section style="display: inline-block;vertical-align: top;width: auto;flex: 100 100 0%;align-self: flex-start;height: auto;box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="font-size: 14px;color: rgb(180, 31, 6);padding: 0px 10px;line-height: 1.7;letter-spacing: 1.5px;box-sizing: border-box;" powered-by="xiumi.us"><p style="text-align: left;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"><em style="box-sizing: border-box;">21.如何对待他人的评价？</em></strong></p></section></section></section></section><section style="text-align: justify;font-size: 14px;color: rgb(62, 62, 62);letter-spacing: 1.5px;line-height: 1.7;padding: 0px 20px;box-sizing: border-box;" powered-by="xiumi.us"><p style="white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;">（1）用理性的心态面对他人的评价，是走向成熟的表现。</p><p style="white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;">（2）要重视他人的态度和评价，也要客观冷静分析，既不能盲从，也不能忽视。</p></section></section></section><section style="margin: 10px 0%;box-sizing: border-box;" powered-by="xiumi.us"><section style="display: inline-block;width: 100%;vertical-align: top;border-width: 1px;border-style: dashed;border-color: rgb(231, 35, 18);background-color: rgb(255, 246, 246);padding: 16px 20px;box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;" powered-by="xiumi.us"><section style="display: flex;flex-flow: row nowrap;box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="display: inline-block;vertical-align: top;width: 15px;flex: 0 0 auto;align-self: flex-start;height: auto;box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="text-align: left;justify-content: flex-start;margin: 9px 0% 0px;transform: translate3d(-5px, 0px, 0px);-webkit-transform: translate3d(-5px, 0px, 0px);-moz-transform: translate3d(-5px, 0px, 0px);-o-transform: translate3d(-5px, 0px, 0px);box-sizing: border-box;" powered-by="xiumi.us"><section style="display: inline-block;width: 9px;height: 9px;vertical-align: top;overflow: hidden;border-width: 0px;border-style: none;border-color: rgb(62, 62, 62);background-color: rgb(255, 206, 82);box-sizing: border-box;"><section><svg viewBox="0 0 1 1" style="float:left;line-height:0;width:0;vertical-align:top;"></svg></section></section></section></section><section style="display: inline-block;vertical-align: top;width: auto;flex: 100 100 0%;align-self: flex-start;height: auto;box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="font-size: 14px;color: rgb(180, 31, 6);padding: 0px 10px;line-height: 1.7;letter-spacing: 1.5px;box-sizing: border-box;" powered-by="xiumi.us"><p style="text-align: left;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"><em style="box-sizing: border-box;">22.正确对待他人评价的方法有哪些？</em></strong></p></section></section></section></section><section style="text-align: justify;font-size: 14px;color: rgb(62, 62, 62);letter-spacing: 1.5px;line-height: 1.7;padding: 0px 20px;box-sizing: border-box;" powered-by="xiumi.us"><p style="white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;">（1）用心聆听：重视他人的评价，不过早下结论。</p><p style="white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;">（2）勇于面对：有勇气面对我们不愿意听到的评价，能更好地看清自己、提升自己。</p><p style="white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;">（3）平静拒绝：平静拒绝别人对我们的过分吹捧或人格贬损，不让这样的评价伤害自己。</p></section></section></section><section style="margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;box-sizing: border-box;" powered-by="xiumi.us"><section style="max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;"><img data-ratio="0.0357698" data-w="643" data-src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_gif/AlBREI3dtiamdX4ghbksyEyoGVWw4icVoIWPqy3BD9r205ocHvlN1bibK1uIYQ89PBHnuermLiaqtsEKOw8tr7AqHA/640?wx_fmt=gif" style="vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; display: initial; visibility: visible !important; height: auto !important; width: 643px !important;" data-type="gif" data-index="21" data-origin-display="" _width="643px" class="__bg_gif" data-order="8" alt="" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_gif/AlBREI3dtiamdX4ghbksyEyoGVWw4icVoIWPqy3BD9r205ocHvlN1bibK1uIYQ89PBHnuermLiaqtsEKOw8tr7AqHA/640?wx_fmt=gif&amp;wxfrom=5&amp;wx_lazy=1" data-fail="0"></section></section><section style="margin: 10px 0%;box-sizing: border-box;" powered-by="xiumi.us"><section style="display: inline-block;width: 100%;vertical-align: top;border-width: 1px;border-style: dashed;border-color: rgb(231, 35, 18);background-color: rgb(255, 246, 246);padding: 16px 20px;box-sizing: border-