rtical-align: top;overflow: hidden;border-width: 0px;border-style: none;border-color: rgb(62, 62, 62);background-color: rgb(255, 206, 82);box-sizing: border-box;"><section><svg viewBox="0 0 1 1" style="float:left;line-height:0;width:0;vertical-align:top;"></svg></section></section></section></section><section style="display: inline-block;vertical-align: top;width: auto;flex: 100 100 0%;align-self: flex-start;height: auto;box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="font-size: 14px;color: rgb(180, 31, 6);padding: 0px 10px;line-height: 1.7;letter-spacing: 1.5px;box-sizing: border-box;" powered-by="xiumi.us"><p style="text-align: left;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"><em style="box-sizing: border-box;">7.有助于建立友谊的方法和技能有哪些？</em></strong></p></section></section></section></section><section style="text-align: justify;font-size: 14px;color: rgb(62, 62, 62);letter-spacing: 1.5px;line-height: 1.7;padding: 0px 20px;box-sizing: border-box;" powered-by="xiumi.us"><p style="white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;">（1）面带微笑。微笑能缩短人与人之间的距离，微笑展示了你的热情、快乐和亲和力。</p><p style="white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;">（2）记住对方的名字。准确地说出对方的名字，会令对方觉得被你关注和尊重。</p><p style="white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;">（3）真诚夸赞。真诚的称赞是对对方的肯定和接纳，对方自然也会愿意接纳你。</p><p style="white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;">（4）寻找共同之处。找到共同的地方，自然就有更多的共同语言。</p><p style="white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;">（5）做一个耐心的倾听者。鼓励对方多谈自己，可以更多地了解对方，也可以让对方感受到他很重要。</p><p style="white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;">（6）保持好奇心。带着好奇走近对方，你便有机会了解对方。</p></section></section></section><section style="margin: 10px 0%;box-sizing: border-box;" powered-by="xiumi.us"><section style="display: inline-block;width: 100%;vertical-align: top;border-width: 1px;border-style: dashed;border-color: rgb(231, 35, 18);background-color: rgb(255, 246, 246);padding: 16px 20px;box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;" powered-by="xiumi.us"><section style="display: flex;flex-flow: row nowrap;box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="display: inline-block;vertical-align: top;width: 15px;flex: 0 0 auto;align-self: flex-start;height: auto;box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="text-align: left;justify-content: flex-start;margin: 9px 0% 0px;transform: translate3d(-5px, 0px, 0px);-webkit-transform: translate3d(-5px, 0px, 0px);-moz-transform: translate3d(-5px, 0px, 0px);-o-transform: translate3d(-5px, 0px, 0px);box-sizing: border-box;" powered-by="xiumi.us"><section style="display: inline-block;width: 9px;height: 9px;vertical-align: top;overflow: hidden;border-width: 0px;border-style: none;border-color: rgb(62, 62, 62);background-color: rgb(255, 206, 82);box-sizing: border-box;"><section><svg viewBox="0 0 1 1" style="float:left;line-height:0;width:0;vertical-align:top;"></svg></section></section></section></section><section style="display: inline-block;vertical-align: top;width: auto;flex: 100 100 0%;align-self: flex-start;height: auto;box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="font-size: 14px;color: rgb(180, 31, 6);padding: 0px 10px;line-height: 1.7;letter-spacing: 1.5px;box-sizing: border-box;" powered-by="xiumi.us"><p style="text-align: left;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"><em style="box-sizing: border-box;">8.为什么友谊需要精心呵护？</em></strong></p></section></section></section></section><section style="text-align: justify;font-size: 14px;color: rgb(62, 62, 62);letter-spacing: 1.5px;line-height: 1.7;padding: 0px 20px;box-sizing: border-box;" powered-by="xiumi.us"><p style="white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;">友谊，就像一株慢慢生长的植物，需要精心养护，经受风雨的洗礼、时间的磨砺。</p></section></section></section><section style="margin: 10px 0%;box-sizing: border-box;" powered-by="xiumi.us"><section style="display: inline-block;width: 100%;vertical-align: top;border-width: 1px;border-style: dashed;border-color: rgb(231, 35, 18);background-color: rgb(255, 246, 246);padding: 16px 20px;box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;" powered-by="xiumi.us"><section style="display: flex;flex-flow: row nowrap;box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="display: inline-block;vertical-align: top;width: 15px;flex: 0 0 auto;align-self: flex-start;height: auto;box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="text-align: left;justify-content: flex-start;margin: 9px 0% 0px;transform: translate3d(-5px, 0px, 0px);-webkit-transform: translate3d(-5px, 0px, 0px);-moz-transform: translate3d(-5px, 0px, 0px);-o-transform: translate3d(-5px, 0px, 0px);box-sizing: border-box;" powered-by="xiumi.us"><section style="display: inline-block;width: 9px;height: 9px;vertical-align: top;overflow: hidden;border-width: 0px;border-style: none;border-color: rgb(62, 62, 62);background-color: rgb(255, 206, 82);box-sizing: border-box;"><section><svg viewBox="0 0 1 1" style="float:left;line-height:0;width:0;vertical-align:top;"></svg></section></section></section></section><section style="display: inline-block;vertical-align: top;width: auto;flex: 100 100 0%;align-self: flex-start;height: auto;box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="font-size: 14px;color: rgb(180, 31, 6);padding: 0px 10px;line-height: 1.7;letter-spacing: 1.5px;box-sizing: border-box;" powered-by="xiumi.us"><p style="text-align: left;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"><em style="box-sizing: border-box;">9.如何呵护友谊？</em></strong></p></section></section></section></section><section style="text-align: justify;font-size: 14px;color: rgb(62, 62, 62);letter-spacing: 1.5px;line-height: 1.7;padding: 0px 20px;box-sizing: border-box;" powered-by="xiumi.us"><p style="white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;">（1）呵护友谊，需要用心去关怀对方。体会朋友的需要，以行动向朋友表达关心和支持。</p><p style="white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;">（2）呵护友谊，需要学会尊重对方。每个人都是独立的个体，要给朋友一些空间，把握好彼此的界限和分寸。朋友之间需要坦诚相待，但这并不意味着毫无保留；给予朋友积极合理的建议，但不要替朋友做决定。</p><p style="white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;">（3）呵护友谊，需要学会正确处理冲突。我们在友谊中获得理解、支持，但也会有矛盾和冲突发生，这是正常现象。冲突发生时，可以相互协商，寻找彼此能够接受的解决办法。</p><p style="white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;">（4）呵护友谊，需要学会正确对待交友中受到的伤害。面对伤害，我们可以选择宽容对方，也可以选择结束这段友谊。</p><p style="white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;">（5）我们还要学会同多数人和睦相处，对所有人以诚相待。</p></section></section></section><section style="margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;box-sizing: border-box;" powered-by="xiumi.us"><section style="max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;"><img data-ratio="0.0357698" data-w="643" data-src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_gif/AlBREI3dtiamdX4ghbksyEyoGVWw4icVoIWPqy3BD9r205ocHvlN1bibK1uIYQ89PBHnuermLiaqtsEKOw8tr7AqHA/640?wx_fmt=gif" style="vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; display: initial; visibility: visible !important; height: auto !important; width: 643px !important;" data-type="gif" data-index="28" data-origin-display="" _width="643px" class="__bg_gif" data-order="12" alt="" src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_gif/AlBREI3dtiamdX4ghbksyEyoGVWw4icVoIWPqy3BD9r205ocHvlN1bibK1uIYQ89PBHnuermLiaqtsEKOw8tr7AqHA/640?wx_fmt=gif&amp;wxfrom=5&amp;wx_lazy=1" data-fail="0"></section></section><section style="margin: 10px 0%;box-sizing: border-box;" powered-by="xiumi.us"><section style="display: inline-block;width: 100%;vertical-align: top;border-width: 1px;border-style: dashed;border-color: rgb(231, 35, 18);background-color: rgb(255, 246, 246);padding: 16px 20px;box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;" powered-by="xiumi.us"><section style="display: flex;flex-flow: row nowrap;box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="display: inline-block;vertical-align: top;width: 15px;flex: 0 0 auto;align-self: flex-start;height: auto;box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="text-align: left;justify-content: flex-start;margin: 9px 0% 0px;transform: translate3d(-5px, 0px, 0px);-webkit-transform: translate3d(-5px, 0px, 0px);-moz-transform: translate3d(-5px, 0px, 0px);-o-transform: translate3d(-5px, 0px, 0px);box-sizing: border-box;" powered-by="xiumi.us"><section style="display: inline-block;width: 9px;height: 9px;vertical-align: top;overflow: hidden;border-width: 0px;border-style: none;border-color: rgb(62, 62, 62);background-color: rgb(255, 206, 82);box-sizing: border-box;"><section><svg viewBox="0 0 1 1" style="float:left;line-height:0;width:0;vertical-align:top;"></svg></section></section></section></section><section style="display: inline-block;vertical-align: top;width: auto;flex: 100 100 0%;align-self: flex-start;height: auto;box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="font-size: 14px;color: rgb(180, 31, 6);padding: 0px 10px;line-height: 1.7;letter-spacing: 1.5px;box-sizing: border-box;" powered-by="xiumi.us"><p style="text-align: justify;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="text-align: left;box-sizing: border-box;"><em style="box-sizing: border-box;">10.处理朋友间冲突的基本策略有哪些？</em></strong><br style="box-sizing: border-box;"></p></section></section></section></section><section style="text-align: justify;font-size: 14px;color: rgb(62, 62, 62);letter-spacing: 1.5px;line-height: 1.7;padding: 0px 20px;box-sizing: border-box;" powered-by="xiumi.us"><p style="white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;">（1）保持冷静。在做决定前先想办法稳定自己的情绪，必要时可以冷处理。</p><p style="white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;">（2）坦诚交流。与朋友坦诚讨论，给朋友也给自己一个解释的机会。</p><p style="white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;">（3）及时处理。时间拖得越久，会使问题的解决越困难。</p><p style="white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;">（4）勇担责任。不把过错全部推给对方。</p><p style="white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;">（5）换位思考。不要只忙于表达自己的想法，试着从对方的角度看问题。</p></section></section></section><section style="margin: 10px 0%;box-sizing: border-box;" powered-by="xiumi.us"><section style="display: inline-block;width: 100%;vertical-align: top;border-width: 1px;border-style: dashed;border-color: rgb(231, 35, 18);background-color: rgb(255, 246, 246);padding: 16px 20px;box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;" powered-by="xiumi.us"><section style="display: flex;flex-flow: row nowrap;box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="display: inline-block;vertical-align: top;width: 15px;flex: 0 0 auto;align-self: flex-start;height: auto;box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="text-align: left;justify-content: flex-start;margin: 9px 0% 0px;transform: translate3d(-5px, 0px, 0px);-webkit-transform: translate3d(-5px, 0px, 0px);-moz-transform: translate3d(-5px, 0px, 0px);-o-transform: translate3d(-5px, 0px, 0px);box-sizing: border-box;" powered-by="xiumi.us"><section style="display: inline-block;width: 9px;height: 9px;vertical-align: top;overflow: hidden;border-width: 0px;border-style: none;border-color: rgb(62, 62, 62);background-color: rgb(255, 206, 82);box-sizing: border-box;"><section><svg viewBox="0 0 1 1" style="float:left;line-height:0;width:0;vertical-align:top;"></svg></section></section></section></section><section style="display: inline-block;vertical-align: top;width: auto;flex: 100 100 0%;align-self: flex-start;height: auto;box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="font-size: 14px;color: rgb(180, 31, 6);padding: 0px 10px;line-height: 1.7;letter-spacing: 1.5px;box-sizing: border-box;" powered-by="xiumi.us"><p style="text-align: justify;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;"><strong style="text-align: left;box-sizing: border-box;"><em style="box-sizing: border-box;">11.如何全面认识网络交友的利与弊？</em></strong><br style="box-sizing: border-box;"></p></section></section></section></section><section style="text-align: justify;font-size: 14px;color: rgb(62, 62, 62);letter-spacing: 1.5px;line-height: 1.7;padding: 0px 20px;box-sizing: border-box;" powered-by="xiumi.us"><p style="white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;">（1）利：互联网为我们提供了一个交友的新平台。网上交往具有虚拟、平等、自主等特点，它超越时空限制，开辟了人际交往的新通道，拓展了交往圈。网上交往可以满足我们的一些心理需要。</p><p style="white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;">（2）弊：互联网开启了通往世界的又一个窗口，但有时却关闭了与他人沟通的心灵之门。虚拟世界的交往，带有很多不确定因素，要有一定的自我保护意识。</p></section></section></section><section style="margin: 10px 0%;box-sizing: border-box;" powered-by="xiumi.us"><section style="display: inline-block;width: 100%;vertical-align: top;border-width: 1px;border-style: dashed;border-color: rgb(231, 35, 18);background-color: rgb(255, 246, 246);padding: 16px 20px;box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="box-sizing: border-box;" powered-by="xiumi.us"><section style="display: flex;flex-flow: row nowrap;box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="display: inline-block;vertical-align: top;width: 15px;flex: 0 0 auto;align-self: flex-start;height: auto;box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="text-align: left;justify-content: flex-start;margin: 9px 0% 0px;transform: translate3d(-5px, 0px, 0px);-webkit-transform: translate3d(-5px, 0px, 0px);-moz-transform: translate3d(-5px, 0px, 0px);-o-transform: translate3d(-5px, 0px, 0px);box-sizing: border-box;" powered-by="xiumi.us"><section style="display: inline-block;width: 9px;height: 9px;vertical-align: top;overflow: hidden;border-width: 0px;border-style: none;border-color: rgb(62, 62, 62);background-color: rgb(255, 206, 82);box-sizing: border-box;"><section><svg viewBox="0 0 1 1" style="float:left;line-height:0;width:0;vertical-align:top;"></svg></section></section></section></section><section style="display: inline-block;vertical-align: top;width: auto;flex: 100 100 0%;align-self: flex-start;height: auto;box-sizing: border-box;"><section style="font-size: 14px;color: rgb(180, 31, 6);padding: 0px 10px;line-height: 1.7;letter-spa